text: Leah Bracknell (born Alison Rosalind Bracknell 12 July 1964 - September 2019) was an English actress. She was best known for her role as Zoe Tate in Emmerdale. She was also a teacher with the British School of Yoga and designs and produces her own line of jewelry. In October 2016, Bracknell revealed that she was suffering from terminal lung cancer.
